name: Into the wild
description:
Gecko’s journey exploring the wilderness.

This artwork is donated to TZ APAC and CoinGecko for Geckocon 2021 by Arya Mularama.

Arya Mularama creates his surreal and satirical artworks using various media. His drawings of the cartoon characters, monsters, doodles and familiar sci-fi characters are influenced by comic books and skateboard culture and the movies and video games of the ‘90s.
